org.eclipse.ptp.core.jobs

Interface IPJobStatus

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IJobStatus

    public interface IPJobStatus
extends IJobStatus
    Extends IJobStatus for parallel jobs. Clients can obtain this interface by adapting an IJobStatus instance.
    Since:
    7.0
